title: Weirdhouse Cinema Rewind: Battle for Endor
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema Rewind: Battle for Endor
description:
The Star Wars franchise is home to many cinematic entries some consider to be unnatural. In this classic episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe discuss the 1985 made-for-TV film “Ewoks: The Battle For Endor,” starring Wilford Brimley and various forest monsters. (originally published 12/4/2020)
